{"tid":2005222,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中美諜戰】中國千人計劃淪入獄計劃 百度、微博全刪變「404」","createTime":"2020-05-07T03:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T10:54:53.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0a1d3d83b3e51f3fb23bc7ab482d50f2dd5a91","tid":2005222,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:33:01.000Z","msg":"【中美諜戰】中國千人計劃淪入獄計劃 百度、微博全刪變「404」<br />\n<br />\n中國於2008年啟動「千人計劃」，吸引大量海外的中國學者返回中國，但如今這一計劃卻銷聲匿迹。過去一年多，美國聯邦調查局（FBI）調查千人學者後，中方已不再提起這項計劃，現在甚至連在中國網絡上都很難搜尋到相關資料，大部份中國著名學府也刪除「千人計劃」的學者資料。<br />\n<br />\n全文請click入蘋果<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200507/FM2CFHQRZ52C6TCD2W5ULGE7IQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200507%2FFM2CFHQRZ52C6TCD2W5ULGE7IQ%2F&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=82ebba21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200507%2FFM2CFHQRZ52C6TCD2W5ULGE7IQ%2F&h=f0eccae9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200507/FM2CFHQRZ52C6TCD2W5ULGE7IQ/</a>"},{"pid":"917a0309cbec3baed931e93da9e214d8908411b0","tid":2005222,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8481aa9917583bca7606219048de6537340f735e","tid":2005222,"uid":242602,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:48:54.000Z","msg":"我記得整紅芯瀏覽器假Google Chrome呃咗幾億嗰條友都係千人計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0593f31720c6e8a32495baa999d1cc2416c9beea","tid":2005222,"uid":15605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8481aa9917583bca7606219048de6537340f735e","tid":2005222,"uid":242602,"like":3,"d